# Agent skills

This repo ships agent skills in `.claude/skills/<name>/SKILL.md` (plus `references/`). Before starting work in an area, read the matching skill file and follow it тАФ the full topic тЖТ skill map is in `AGENTS.md` ("Skills" section).

Quick routes: WP task classification тЖТ `wordpress-router` ┬╖ plugin dev тЖТ `wp-plugin-development` ┬╖ WooCommerce/HPOS/gateways тЖТ `wp-woocommerce-dev` ┬╖ REST endpoints тЖТ `wp-rest-api` ┬╖ PHPStan тЖТ `wp-phpstan` ┬╖ WP-CLI ops тЖТ `wp-wpcli-and-ops` ┬╖ backend perf тЖТ `wp-performance` ┬╖ frontend perf тЖТ `core-web-vitals`/`performance` ┬╖ PHP security review тЖТ `wp-security-review` + `differential-review`/`insecure-defaults`/`variant-analysis` ┬╖ migrations тЖТ `wp-migration-upgrade-review` ┬╖ modern CSS/JS тЖТ `modern-web-guidance` ┬╖ a11y тЖТ `accessibility` ┬╖ SEO тЖТ `seo` ┬╖ email HTML тЖТ `email-html-mjml`.

This suite uses **Elementor only тАФ no Gutenberg/block-editor development**.
